Description

British Standards BS 381C Light Purple Brown 449 Aerosol Spray Paint

When it comes to quality and price, Your Spray Paints is always the best choice. With over 35 years of industry experience, we provide the UK with innovative and high-quality spray-painting products. Available to both Public & Trade. Our British Standards BS 381C Light Purple Brown 449 Aerosol Spray Paint is professionally mixed by our team of technical experts using the very best ingredients. The Aerosol Canisters are the best quality for spraying and each aerosol has a volume of 400ml and accept all our colours in either 1K or 2K paint and in Full, Semi, Satin & Matt gloss levels.

If you have any queries with respect to this product please ask a member of staff for help on 0800 530 0375 or customerservices@yourspraypaints.com

*Please note – These are mixed colours, colour accuracy should be checked before application. No responsibility for colour differences can be accepted after use.
